(## Run On Android Phone) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Enable Developer Options on the phone.) Tj
T*
(2. Enable USB Debugging.) Tj
T*
(3. Connect the phone by USB.) Tj
T*
(4. Accept the debugging prompt on the phone.) Tj
T*
(5. Check device detection:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```powershell) Tj
T*
(adb devices) Tj
T*
(flutter devices) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6. Run the app:) Tj
T*
() Tj
