(```powershell) Tj
T*
(cd C:\\Users\\kaasi\\Downloads\\jun\\med_reminder_app) Tj
T*
(flutter run) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## ESP32 AP Mode Notes) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Connect the phone to the ESP32 Wi-Fi network.) Tj
T*
(- Keep the ESP32 IP as `192.168.4.1`.) Tj
T*
(- If the phone disconnects because there is no internet, turn off mobile data or disable ) Tj
T*
(automatic network switching.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## Android Manifest Requirements) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The app uses plain HTTP to the ESP32 local IP, so Android needs:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- `android.permission.INTERNET`) Tj
T*
(- `android:usesCleartextTraffic="true"`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(These are already added in `android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
